TI  - Perceptions of ChatGPT and the Complexity of Its Impact Among Higher Education Students: Evidence Across Ten Countries of Latin America and Europe
T1  - Perceptions of ChatGPT and the Complexity of Its Impact Among Higher Education Students: Evidence Across Ten Countries of Latin America and Europe
JO  - Educational Process International Journal
T2  - Educational Process International Journal
